Smart Computing December 2012

Smart Computing Magazine helps users of all skill levels stay up-to-date and improve their PC productivity. It provides easy-to-follow tutorials that cover hardware, software, internet, and troubleshooting issues. Each issue of Smart Computing contains product reviews and much more, all in a plain-English writing style that you won't find anywhere else.
